{
  "stem": "8892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they look strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They look healthy looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was assigned to the assembly line where the bullets groove we were doing, and then a cap came on it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my sister was putting the powder in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was in front of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we're still together, the five cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody's sick, thank god.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is already-- we're doing this from September, end of September-- no it's beginning of September.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the ration was OK, that it was holding us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the cold weather started to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And already in there in November, beginning of November, October we had snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And our shoes was not a shoe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember having a wooden shoe with about two pieces of-- of rags around it that are as some kind of socks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is-- we marched to the factory, I would say about 3 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A few, long, long march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was a beautiful forest, and trees, you know, that beautiful German evergreens on two sides of the road.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we're marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we never see village people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We never see anybody except who worked in the munition factory, and who was in a camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in there, too, we had one rotten officer, who was-- we called her like a lesbian, mannish and mean.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And oh, she enjoyed just somebody getting out of line, and hit them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But then we had a young girl who was 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we think, girls, if she was watching us, because she had to be in a barrack with us, nighttime too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when she would have a chance she would talk to some of the girls who fluently talked German, and telling us how she's 18 and she's going to have a baby.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
